{
  "texts": [
    "AAC systems could become more responsive and adaptive, while AI-powered telepractice platforms may increase accessibility for clients in rural or underserved communities.",
    "These advancements promise to expand both the efficacy and reach of technology-driven interventions in SLP.",
    "SLPs play a role in public health by improving communication environments and managing care at the population level.",
    "AI can contribute to these efforts by analyzing anonymized EHRs to identify service gaps, track therapy outcomes, and inform policy.",
    "Administrative dashboards powered by AI can support clinic and schoolbased interventions and provide real-time updates for insurers."
  ]
}